Part -1

Basic
: docker version
: docker -v
: docker info
: docker --help
: docker login
————————————
Images
: docker images
: docker pull
: docker rmi - remove images
————————————
Containers
: docker ps -shows all running containers
: docker run -runs container with c id and tags like 'it'
: docker start 
: docker stop
————————————
System
: docker stats
: docker system df disc memory
: docker system prune deltes all images with '-a' deletes all containes and files whoch are not used.
